deck: Special silent issue.
description:
After a combined 40 years of working in comics, Marcos and I have attempted our very first silent issue with todays release of BARRIER #3. The whole team is really proud of this one (Marcos and Muntsas talented young son Nil even contributed to a page!), so we hope you dig it. And if youve missed our previous installments of this sci-fi exploration of language and immigration, theyre always available to download for absolutely any price you think is fair exclusively at Panelsyndicate.com, along with all of THE PRIVATE EYE, our special WALKING DEAD one-shot, and the best issue yet of UNIVERSE! from Albert Monteys. Happy Holidays, everyone!

Plot Summary

After a brief separation, and a pretty intense dream, Liddy and Oscar reunite and continue their attempts to survive the alien experience.
